'''Docking Bay 107''' was a [[Hangar/Legends|docking bay]] located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Dandrian]]. ''[[Carpagian]]'' was cleared to land in this bay when it was carrying a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] who were attempting to contact [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Joser]].

